headline: Is EQT (EQT) Still Attractive After A 72.9% Three Year Share Price Gain

The share price last closed at US$54.83, with returns of 9.1% over the past week, 2.5% over the last month, 2.6% year to date, 3.9% over one year, 72.9% over three years and a very large gain over five years.
